Jeannie Gaffigan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeannie_Gaffigan 0 Jeanne Louise Gaffigan (née Noth) is an American actress, producer, and comedy writer. She is married to comedian Jim Gaffigan. She is best known as a writer and executive producer for The Jim Gaffigan Show, a show loosely based on her own family life with her husband.
